---
title: Lamb and DIY Tomato Jam Burger with Feta Aioli, Cucumber and Kale Slaw
description: A thing of such delicious, dribble-down-your-chin simplicity, the noble burger can be re-invented time and time again to create the most divine dinnertime results. For this little incarnation, we've taken ground lamb and thrown in a Greek twist with a kick.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lamb-and-diy-tomato-jam-burger-890717cc.jpg
